				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Playing &quot;Hide 'n Sneak&quot; is probably the most useful thing I have found in a rouge's life below 10th level. I walked all the way from Freeport to Qeynos unarmed and unharmed using this tactic. Makes a rouge an excellent scout to send ahead into unknown zones. Start by getting a successful sneak, then go for a successful hide. Both must be successful then go ahead and walk anywhere you want unseen. Anyone else had any luck with this?
