			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Sneak works well with this, to make up for prices, hold a crude stein for +CHA. The best trick for rogues, however, comes with your ability to loot. Pickpockets while in group, and if you are high enough, disarm. You can make a fortune, and the group is none the wiser. I only do this when there is a ninja looter in the group, but if you need cash, the Rogue is never on short supply. One more thing, remember never to pay more than 50pp for ANY Ravenscale. Rogues are more commonly doing this and slowly, but surely, wizards are KSing the lizzys in cazic less, and Prices are more reasonable . (Even though AGI is far better than DEX)<BR>
<BR>
Vasandralov<BR>
Rogue - Hidden Fighting Level<BR>
